{"tid":599050,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"受傷了？GD 當兵「腳綁護套照」曝光，粉絲好心疼！","createTime":"2018-03-20T05:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T14:07:34.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7797982d5f8e9af6186054aab018cc4dad71902e","tid":599050,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/76816/5aaf5b21534b0.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F76816%2F5aaf5b21534b0.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=27fc2e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n29 歲的韓國天團 BIGBANG 隊長 G-DRAGON 權志龍（GD）於上月27日入伍從軍，除了令粉絲大為不捨之外，關於 GD 在軍中的一舉一動更是令大眾十分關心。而昨晚從社交網站上流出的新照中，GD腳上穿著拖鞋戴著護套，令粉絲十分擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/76816/5aaf5875b9a59.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F76816%2F5aaf5875b9a59.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=d43761bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼目前 GD 正在江原道鐵源陸軍第 3 師團白骨部隊接受新兵受訓，接受完新兵訓練後 GD 將以陸軍身份被派往其他部隊繼續服役，並於 2019 年 11 月26 日退伍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/76816/5aaf5875bf800.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F76816%2F5aaf5875bf800.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=a780773b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼而昨晚，社交網站公開了GD的近況照，當中 GD 穿著灰色的訓練服坐地上，頭戴軍隊貝雷帽，腳穿綠色的軍隊拖鞋。他在一開始就破掉了Federer兩個發球分，迅速將比分拉開到6:1領先，與其他同袍相比 GD 的腳上明顯戴上了護套，令粉絲十分擔心他的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/76816/5aaf56dd6847c.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F76816%2F5aaf56dd6847c.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=01230c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼雖然作為一個軍人，受傷是在所難免，但是除了有可能是當兵訓練時受傷外，令人擔心的是，外媒報導這也極有可能是 GD 於 2013 年在大阪開個人演唱會期間，右腳踝曾經受傷卻忍痛開唱所遺留的隱患，令粉絲相當不捨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/76816/5aaf56dd6e1ab.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F76816%2F5aaf56dd6e1ab.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=b5e28f64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5cb1a93d8a895da0c446e061efafad6fb9a1a53a","tid":599050,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52340a09e0bc9ed108322fae4092e9ce53a9fc68","tid":599050,"uid":90633,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"咁耐以黎都唔知原來GD網球咁勁"},{"pid":"dfcc6ee4a9ea1facb321b9d7c8a778bf7dd17d6a","tid":599050,"uid":73,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:43:49.000Z","msg":"GD 頭戴軍隊貝雷帽，腳穿綠色的軍隊拖鞋，在一開始就破掉了Federer兩個發球分，迅速將比分拉開到6:1領先"},{"pid":"f7b2ac0ed1e0523447d78a25f30a65bda3eb9008","tid":599050,"uid":2772,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n睇錯腳綁護照....<br />\n搵左好撚耐都睇唔到"},{"pid":"43b7b03fbb6484a148ca40480d4134143239182a","tid":599050,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:45:15.000Z","msg":"韓國眼鏡鋪應該都搵唔少"},{"pid":"fffc049438be817445e81de70304a9092013e6ef","tid":599050,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52340a09e0bc9ed108322fae4092e9ce53a9fc68","tid":599050,"uid":90633,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"咁耐以黎都唔知原來GD網球咁勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"費達拿都唔係佢對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09185eb361d64c1312a075b2362a1c8023e0c192","tid":599050,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfcc6ee4a9ea1facb321b9d7c8a778bf7dd17d6a","tid":599050,"uid":